Module dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform
Package dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform.registry

Interface ResourceReaderFactory<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - resource type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ResourceReaderFactory.ActionResource, ResourceReaderFactory.AudioResource, ResourceReaderFactory.RenderableResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionResourceReaderFactory, AudioResourceReaderFactory, RenderableResourceReaderFactory
    public interface ResourceReaderFactory<T>
    Generates resource readers attached to a Registry reading resources from strings. Clients can obtain a module-path-loaded instance of a resource reader using get(Class, Registry) with the relevant provider type.
